result.name: Cafe Prince Royal

reviews.text: Portion could be a bit bigger, I like the Expresso tonic the best. This is my first time having such a coffee and it just taste perfect and looks cool as well. Simple but good.

AVOID! Staff have serious attitude! I usually go to this cafe almost every Sat, today I walked in and it was crowded but there were some people that had seats available. I asked if i can join another table, the staff walked over pointed and complained to their customer that I wanted to share the table. I ordered, but saw some seats were free at another table. I walked over to ask if I could join, but the STAFF STARTED YELLING AT ME IN FRONT OF ALL OTHER CUSTOMERS. LADY! LADY! YOUR TABLE IS THERE! WTF! HOW RUDE CAN YOU BE? I asked for my money back immediately, and will never visit that cafe again!

$98 for a coffee and pasta during noon.  I’ll rate both the coffee and pasta a 6 out of 10
They use frozen shrimp without cleaning the intestines. Scallops were the smallest size scallops 0.5-0.8cm.  If you go to Maxim Group restos, you can get much higher quality with same or lower price.  Can’t expect too high at Prince Edward tho
food is good, but very strange that no dessert available after 6pm

If you are looking for a decent hand drop coffee this isn’t the place. They don’t offer single origin choices....

But still offering light foods with nice environment thou....

result.name: Cafe Prince Royal

reviews.text: Portion could be a bit bigger, I like the Expresso tonic the best. This is my first time having such a coffee and it just taste perfect and looks cool as well. Simple but good.
食物非常新鮮……可惜欠缺下午茶選擇
其實餐廳硬件很好，食物也好食，唯一敗筆是其中一名短髮中性女員工。 態度不單其差，不停趕客咁。 見滿客亦沒有出去告訴等待的人該等還是怎樣，對d客呼呼喝喝。 更甚的是，當了cafe是她屋企，不停對其他同事趕粗口。 明明文青系cafe即刻變左太子劈場咁。希望老闆可以改善一下吧，從餐廳既陳設，猜想老闆也是有心人，別讓一個員工浪費了一番心血。
傾偈好地方。咖啡好飲，有芒果辣椒班尼，特別！
環境好舒服，食物也新鮮及熱，即煮即熱。
